casebody.data:
No. 08-1592. James M. Maloney, Petitioner v. Kathleen A. Rice, District Attorney, Nassau County, New York. 561 U.S. 1040, 130 S. Ct. 3541,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1119,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5539. June 29, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit for further consideration in light of McDonald v. Chicago, 561 U.S. 742, 130 S. Ct. 3020, 177 L. Ed. 2d 894 (2010).

Justice Soto-mayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 554 F.3d 56.
